{"tid":1655854,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今次陳彦霖既死我地要以搵出真相為目標","createTime":"2019-10-15T09:24:38.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-15T10:05:12.000Z","uid":9131,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"1d875179a7fb0ddd54527f9891395c79172539ca","tid":1655854,"uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T09:24:38.000Z","msg":"由頭到尾hkdi既行為都<span style=\"color: red;\">好奇怪！！</span><br />\n以依家現時既科技根本唔可能會<span style=\"color: red;\">咁低清，重複有跳秒問題，中途暫停既問題</span><br />\n當大家都不斷發酵白衫人後 突然又有新片出證明白衫人入去嗰陣係冇做到任何事 然後條片又斷左 然後又有新疑點就係白衫人有冇出lift <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">我地心態必須改變！！！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">1. 唔可以再跌入循環</span></span><br />\n假設我地再不停發酵話證明唔到個白衫人冇出lift喎<br />\n但之後又有新片出黎證明個白衫人真係冇出lift 大家又再一次炒車 但相反如果個白衫人係有出lift咁都未必證明到咩 所以我地要繼續要求佢交出完整既片段外 更重要係搵其他證據 例如其他角度什至地方既cctv 還原事實真相<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">2. 暫時唔好過份將呢件事拉落黑警警暴</span></span><br />\n我知大家都知呢件事如果真係被殺既最大機會行兇者既身份<br />\n但同831 新屋嶺唔同既係 今次既可能性確實多少少<br />\n而且確實大家已經輕微炒左少少車 炒車唔緊要 但我地唔可以炒到令啲狗可以因為今次番盤再扮哂野話新屋嶺831係大家過份幻想<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黑警依家已經冇認受性 我地要靠自己幫手足還源真相 如果有兇手 藍絲黑警咩都好 必定要清算<br />\n<br />\n要做既野冇改變 一樣所有證據我全部要<br />\n但心態微調 唔可以俾班垃圾有任何翻盤機會<br />\n唔可以俾佢地帶住我地行<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">為手足還原真相</span></span>"},{"pid":"2522699bf013416ef9b28e19aee9ee9a4be94bc7","tid":1655854,"uid":172638,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T09:24:53.000Z","msg":"提提大家今日同嚟緊有咩活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/EWwdQSV.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FEWwdQSV.jpg&h=dac2fb28&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/YEYDhxW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FYEYDhxW.jpg&h=6daa77db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s1ngOED.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs1ngOED.jpg&h=f7b0fc33&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲有10&middot;20九龍見<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BHcgOFM.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBHcgOFM.jpg&h=4465099d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d90f8a5626ddba0418fff29c2a87c3ec22b15563","tid":1655854,"uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T09:25:38.000Z","msg":"推俾多啲人睇 麻煩大家"},{"pid":"39b13ac222a0f2276bec7bda74abc648194ec2ae","tid":1655854,"uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T09:26:00.000Z","msg":"多角度搵真相"},{"pid":"211b1dea28ddcd64adaa6d13d1ccbf68b6dfa133","tid":1655854,"uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T09:26:10.000Z","msg":"車can"},{"pid":"ae1cc7d44db7273bb6febbe658e6170e1af68cc3","tid":1655854,"uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"211b1dea28ddcd64adaa6d13d1ccbf68b6dfa133","tid":1655854,"uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T09:26:10.000Z","msg":"車can"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T09:26:22.000Z","msg":"Cam"},{"pid":"6adcfbd07629139a7e35c520aecd582d67f21124","tid":1655854,"uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T09:26:41.000Z","msg":"海旁cctv!"},{"pid":"7fc119470946196ea530de4eb8ed1d4177cda430","tid":1655854,"uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T09:27:01.000Z","msg":"邊層出lift cctv"},{"pid":"93ce0d226ee4c63c08e9b61f25e72fd20509bb5d","tid":1655854,"uid":21028,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T09:27:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"0259e8d9aad37ca20dfc1eac864ddac373a1343a","tid":1655854,"uid":9131,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-15T09:27:25.000Z","msg":"一定要多角度"},{"pid":"d570ba3ddd86f8b5a653ff6ca01d9ee6a683e7d9","tid":1655854,